title: Thales Payshield 10K NTP
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/Payshield
license: Proprietary
distribution: Proprietary
description:
 This check monitors the NTP (Network Time Protocol) status of Thales Payshield 10K devices.

 The output of the check plugin provides:

 - NTP Offset (ms)
 - NTP Stratum
 - NTP Peer Status

 Long output of the check plugin provides:

 - NTP Synchronization Status
 - NTP Server Address
 - NTP Last Update Time

inventory:
 This check does not create inventory entries.
